ks of smallcap companies the firm employs quantitative analysis to create its portfolios it employs a combination of inhouse and external research to make its investments the firm typically invests in companies in consumer and financial services sectors red mountain capital partners llc was founded in january  and is based in los angeles california  santa monica boulevardsuite los angeles ca united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwredmtncapcom key executives for red mountain capital partners llc mr t willem mesdag jd founder managing partner managing director and chief investment officer age  ms amrita mapara controller principal  chief financial officer mr john christopher teets partner managing partner portfolio manager  chief compliance officer age  mr john k hill iii partner and head of business development mr patrick lally partner compensation as of fiscal year  red mountain capital partners llc key developments investor calls for deckers outdoor to put itself up for sale mar   deckers outdoor corporation nysedeck is up about  in early afterhours trade after red mountain capital partners llc which owns about  of deckers stock said it has sent a letter to the company requesting it put itself up for sale red mountain urges irobot to explore strategic alternatives including sale dec   in a letter to colin angle the chairman and chief executive office of irobot corporation nasdaqgsirbt red mountain capital partners llc suggested irobot to explore strategic alternatives for the defense and security business discontinue the remote presence business focus on the high growth home robots business and the consumer endmarket allocate capital with discipline and an intense focus on riskadjusted returns and address significant lapses in corporate governance in addition red mountain said that the board should consider all other paths to maximize shareholder value including a sale of irobot as an alternative to the implementation of the proposed value enhancement plan similar